{"tid":36914,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾家琪懸疑短故","createTime":"2016-12-13T04:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T07:23:31.000Z","uid":63439,"like":27,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e35c45def2f5707258d06e7e41cbf723f5c52c4","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"1.\t父與子<br />\n孩子: 爸爸, 你想要我嗎?<br />\n爸爸: 可以不要嗎?<br />\n孩子:那麼我游慢一點吧.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.\t情人<br />\n小明: 小麗, 雖然你拒絕了我1000次, 但我仍然很愛你<br />\n小麗: 放心, 我不會再拒絕你<br />\n當晚, 小明去世了<br />\n<br />\n3.\t的士<br />\n小明: 真幸運, 這個時候還有的士<br />\n司機: 我等了你很久了<br />\n小明: 司機, 我的家的方向在另一邊&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想欣賞鍾家琪第一個長篇懸疑故事《空中驚魂錄》，請到以下link :<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/35181/page/1 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F35181%2Fpage%2F1%20&d=bTZKz13pax5JT9y%2F6kiqxQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=841aba2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/35181/page/1 </a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家想重溫第二個長篇懸疑故事《紅寶石》，請到以下link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/36435/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F36435%2Fpage%2F1&d=bTZKz13pax5JT9y%2F6kiqxQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=7d6618fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/36435/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n如果大家想重溫第三個長篇懸疑故事《猩猩》，請到以下link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/36768/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F36768%2Fpage%2F1&d=bTZKz13pax5JT9y%2F6kiqxQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=5f47518e\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/36768/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4c1806fed10ae30a4dd0ea2eeacd4dd3f80861e4","tid":36914,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fa8d8ddd638ab29105a02ba7d4f9b541f17d2a","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"4. 愛的表現 <br />\n爸爸:小明, 你在做什麼?<br />\n小明正站在一隻小狗後面, 身體正在不斷震抖著, 小狗則發出無助的呼叫聲:<br />\n小明: 我愛小狗, 平時我見爸爸媽媽都是這樣的<br />\n爸爸:&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n5. 減肥<br />\n小明:小麗, 你在割脈自殺?<br />\n小麗: 當然不是, 老師今天說人體7成重量都是由水組成, 我現在是減肥.<br />\n小明:&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"0e2207a463ed44149c3ce72819a06493cb462f20","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"6. <br />\n今天天氣明明有攝氏30度, 街上的行人卻都穿著厚厚的羊毛衣<br />\n<br />\n7. 你是誰?<br />\n某人:你是誰?<br />\n小明:我是小明, 你又是誰?<br />\n某人: 我是小明<br />\n小明定一定神, 才發現前面只有一面鏡子<br />\n<br />\n8. 六合彩<br />\n小明: 好耶, 我中了六合彩<br />\n某人:你肯定?<br />\n小明:當然!不信給你看看<br />\n某人:對你中了, 我都中了<br />\n小明:你中了什麼?<br />\n某人:你看看插在你身上的刀, 和我手上拿著的彩票"},{"pid":"d35b749258c983dc1a6cd68009d59bfbc8f75144","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"9：誰是魚？<br />\n<br />\n小明：魚缸𥚃的魚真慘，沒有自由。<br />\n老闆：小明，早上給你的工作做好了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n10: 誤會<br />\n<br />\n上帝：你今天不宜出門，否則必有大禍。<br />\n先生：知道。<br />\n結果第二日，先生因為家中失火被活活燒死。<br />\n當他再見上帝時，問：上帝，你不是說我不宜出門嗎？<br />\n上帝：我有跟你說過，你適宜在家嗎？"},{"pid":"53b93a73b09abeeb052eeac15f5720d42653943b","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"11. 女朋友<br />\n<br />\n媽媽: 呀仔!你幾時帶女朋友回家讓我見下呢?<br />\n仔: 我都沒有女朋友! <br />\n仔心想: 我就算有都是男朋友&hellip;<br />\n媽媽:那麼昨天我見那拖著你的女孩子是誰?"},{"pid":"02a2aa91d21cf08e739be4bb3da1e1af870ba11e","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"12. 萬聖節<br />\n<br />\n小明: 小李, 你今天的造型很認真呢!<br />\n小李: 真的嗎?<br />\n小李雙手將頭抬起,讓頭頸分離<br />\n小明:&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"d3905d3729d9259a7cc4eb02c38d4f80f0a4b1f1","tid":36914,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"幾好睇"},{"pid":"e9d7ffc30fb5487013aec8f93490d842e93f554d","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好睇</blockquote><br />\nYEAH!!!!THX"},{"pid":"f3cdba83c73da26240d51f2bf056443f21980f56","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"13. 爸爸<br />\n<br />\n小明: 爸爸, 如果有人成日蝦你,你會怎樣做?<br />\n爸爸:一槍打死佢<br />\n小明舉起手槍對著爸爸: 謝謝你<br />\n砰&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"f255ebb29a0303e6bd494dd1cd3fcdc2ab197c9a","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"14. 姐姐<br />\n<br />\n爸爸: 小明, 你在跟誰談天?<br />\n小明: 小柔姐姐<br />\n爸爸暗驚:誰是小柔姐姐?<br />\n小明: 她說今晚要帶爸爸走了."},{"pid":"0f0d6ce893d0ce6d32e6f7479871c8c641aac38e","tid":36914,"uid":15757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興趣"},{"pid":"a855d096123f53d2649c2ea8f80d746bf443abc5","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073e7012b1d4f90899f0dcecae62a32f02a4a857","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:58:12.000Z","msg":"15.\t葬禮<br />\n<br />\n小明：這班人在哭甚麼呢？<br />\n(等我行近些，看清楚)<br />\n(下！這不是我太太、還有我的孩子&hellip;&hellip;)<br />\n小明：慢著！為甚麼我的孩子手上捧著我的照片！"},{"pid":"d53e2f1a54081af72655a958abd3b5b9c4682935","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"16.\t滿座<br />\n<br />\n司機：沒有座位了，坐下一班吧！<br />\n小明：甚麼？<br />\n司機：聽不到我說嗎？沒有座位啦！<br />\n接著，小明看著空空的小巴飛馳而去。"},{"pid":"fde4f7704ed53c1428af6fb675411d294fd199a4","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:56:20.000Z","msg":"17. 誰是寵物?<br />\n<br />\n小明: 狗仔, 你過來.<br />\n(為什麼小狗沒有反應的呢?)<br />\n小明: 小狗終於走過來了.<br />\n小明: 唉!為什麼狗帶會掛在我頸上呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18. 加數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老師: 小明, 這房間中有幾多人呢?<br />\n<br />\n小明:三個<br />\n<br />\n老師:一加一等於幾多?<br />\n<br />\n小明:二<br />\n<br />\n老師: 房間裡只有我和你, 怎會有三個人?<br />\n<br />\n小明: 老師, 你算少了站在你旁邊的那位"},{"pid":"7e78698501e5284449ab6f49e165f4ac1dd9107b","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"5正5負😂😂"},{"pid":"271cc3922530631fa6dfb9ca697dce8e04ba6169","tid":36914,"uid":66634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"好睇<br />\n但唔明6、7、11<br />\n等睇大家分析"},{"pid":"8f8a67f416955928382eb09671efcdc419c30d8e","tid":36914,"uid":47845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5正5負😂😂</blockquote><br />\n俾多個正"},{"pid":"0808fad7514e6e55a40a0fd4ed57e7c7f00f82be","tid":36914,"uid":47845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5正5負😂😂</blockquote><br />\n俾多個正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6aa80cf6a2e1113ab3fff10f08c3c920488ca44","tid":36914,"uid":59984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"幾正<br />\nmore please <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5816bb850ad3367f685dc9a9da564d6d8eb9951","tid":36914,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"30度果個改做d 15度短裙西 好似貼地d"},{"pid":"e35bab2df1014cc7cd0f1f3ce4efe9bd9ae701c9","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T23:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30度果個改做d 15度短裙西 好似貼地d</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed586e6e3d371fc59beda7e1aab26da9f0efad0","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"11. 私家車<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n早上來到了停車場，發現在自己的汽車由左軚變成右軚。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n向看看其他的汽車，他們一樣由左軚變成右軚；<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n奇怪的是，其他司機沒有我那種奇怪的感覺；"},{"pid":"6e60b85ee05be03015e53ce1000f467f724ec477","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"19.巴士<br />\n<br />\n今日坐巴士，坐在樓上的中排位置。<br />\n<br />\n漸漸，我開始覺得有點問題。<br />\n<br />\n前面的座位排數好像越來越多，最後幾乎看不到盡頭........."},{"pid":"5191617329dde4ad570d4aee58681ac69e6ed52c","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"20 :撞車<br />\n<br />\n媽的！隨着我的呼叫聲，我駕著的車子，撞上了一位正在過的行人，他被車子撞到拋上半空，再跌在地上，再也動也不動。<br />\n<br />\n很快我也被強勁的衝擊力撞暈了。<br />\n<br />\n過了很久，我終於醒來了。<br />\n<br />\n但很快我又暈過去了，因為我看見眼前的醫生，就是剛才被我車子撞到的男人。"},{"pid":"d482a591076b6d33bbed3c723259ce60c4af2ff3","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"21：西瓜<br />\n<br />\n今天買一個西瓜回來吃。<br />\n<br />\n奇怪的是，這個西瓜是蜜瓜味。"},{"pid":"8893967849d7a9ef1308e34fd6edd5dde7352a8c","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"22:書<br />\n<br />\n小明真乖，已經看了一整天書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當媽媽打算看看小明正在看什麼書時，才發覺這本書是沒有字的...........只是一頁頁白紙......."},{"pid":"c162351c03487711629a09db2131aa3d4d3814c3","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"23：禮物<br />\n<br />\n女友：小明，你為什麼知道我希望收到這條手鏈作為禮物呢？<br />\n<br />\n小明：你昨天跟我行街時，在商店中望了這條手鍊很久，我當然知道。<br />\n<br />\n女友：我昨天可沒有跟你逛街........"},{"pid":"ea68b875f1019805214aac2a2611ab82905212d9","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:36:04.000Z","msg":"24：見工<br />\n<br />\n老闆：小明，請問你什麼時候可以上班呢？<br />\n<br />\n小明：我馬上就可以上班。<br />\n<br />\n老闆：很好！<br />\n<br />\n接着，老闆就從口袋裏取出手槍，一槍就將小明殺死。<br />\n<br />\n小明手上拿着的應徴廣告寫著「死神的助手」。"},{"pid":"73226ea30373774393d4e03d1ccf52d2d5f93426","tid":36914,"uid":22940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好睇<br />\n但唔明6、7、11<br />\n等睇大家分析</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"98b24eb8d3e9f57fa0c3071fedce3e233a1fb660","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好睇<br />\n但唔明6、7、11<br />\n等睇大家分析</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這些故事，每個人👀有不同感覺😊😊建議你看時代入其中，你就會有獨一無二的感覺🤓🤓"},{"pid":"0bc8464e0dd1d52508bbfb91157a222c6a2ad670","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"大家有冇故事交流下😊😊😊"},{"pid":"679aa72492822a5b2f23c9b5550744a097b61820","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:30:53.000Z","msg":"25: 新屋<br />\n<br />\n小明：小李，你要搬走？<br />\n<br />\n小李：對的，我已經買了新居了。<br />\n<br />\n小明：你的新居在哪裏，找天我要來參觀。<br />\n<br />\n小李就將新居的地址寫給了小明。<br />\n<br />\n隔了數天後，小明按着小李的地址前往探望。去到的時候，才發覺這裏是一片墓碑........"},{"pid":"122ec2f7ac04589dd14736d44a291f02ac089b3c","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"26：下班<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早上，小明伸一伸懶腰，就睜開眼睛說：「i唉又要上班了！」<br />\n<br />\n隔了一會兒，小明聽到一把聲音，彷彿對他說：「終於下班了。」<br />\n<br />\n問題就來了，小明一向是一人居住，房間裏面沒有其他人。<br />\n<br />\n小明覺得奇怪，想確定自己沒有聽錯，於是再說說：「唉又要上班了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔了一會，那把男聲又說道：「終於下班了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這次小明聽得十分清楚，那把聲音是從自己的身體發出來的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＊難道我們的身體日間是由我們控制，晚上卻由另一個軀體控制？"},{"pid":"9b9db8ba6d1bfad8d7e85602de18e668a845ef29","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"27：獅子山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小明：媽！我終於登上獅子山頭了！<br />\n<br />\n突然，小明聽到地下傳來的一把聲音：別踏著我的頭！"},{"pid":"e6e047dfee7d77c95b3baa000287ebb5cd808aca","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"28：隧道<br />\n<br />\n由上環開進西隧，離開時發現去了沙田！"},{"pid":"01b2934e358969b8fd52e4c4b54392c6978df7fc","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"29：負皮<br />\n<br />\n《鍾家琪懸疑短故》咁好睇，點解有咁多負皮？"},{"pid":"75923ca4b7af79242654280abf804aeffef8bf2a","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"30 : 電梯<br />\n<br />\n一如平日，小明看着電梯門緩緩關上，向着地下進發。<br />\n<br />\n30樓、29樓、28樓、27樓.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電梯門在27樓是打開，小明下意識向門外一望，馬上驚呆了，因為.......正要入電梯的男子竟然和自己長著一樣的模樣！"},{"pid":"6f7ce51367b11a4ab647417bc3830ecb7c5ed404","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"31：電梯（2）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「等等.....亅，隨著一位女士的呼叫聲，電梯門又再打開了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電梯內只有兩位男士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正當女士拉着一位只有三歲大的小朋友進入電梯時，那位小朋友不斷拉着媽媽說，說：「媽媽！不要進去，𥚃面已經擠滿人了。」<br />\n<br />\n媽媽很奇怪，就說：「裏面只有兩位哥哥，不要玩，馬上進去吧！」<br />\n<br />\n「媽媽！裏面真的是擠滿人了！難道你看不到嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n相信這時感到最驚慌的，一定是在電梯裏的那兩位男士！"},{"pid":"636124637adce3ae4f2939afa42bb23ff6045b19","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:15:44.000Z","msg":"32：消失<br />\n<br />\n今天的地鐵車廂格外擠擁。<br />\n<br />\n小明站在車廂的中間，乘客從四方八面地向他擠過來。<br />\n<br />\n人越來越多，人與人之間的距離越來越少，小明的身體開始被其他人夾得將三文魚般。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奇怪的是，那些人彷彿看不見小明，小明好像不存在的樣子，最後小明的身體終於被其他乘客吞噬了。地鐵車廂內，再也沒有他的位置"},{"pid":"f3c60774083792bb48582f6af608e75fb69e1013","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"33：六合彩<br />\n<br />\n小明：哈哈！我中了頭獎！三千萬！<br />\n<br />\n小明拿著獎券到了馬會領獎。<br />\n<br />\n接待員看一看獎券，就對小明說：「先生，你這張獎券是下期用的。」"},{"pid":"8a717b2e27f755637777431cd8ba811a886afa04","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"32：小心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老人：小明，你今天上班要小心！<br />\n<br />\n正在街上行走的小明，被不認識的老人家接着說，就感到十分不解，便問老人：「為什麼今天我要特別小心呢？」<br />\n<br />\n老人拉起自己的褲腳，露出義肢，說：「你知道嗎，我的腿變成這樣，就是因為你今天將會的意外。」"},{"pid":"66ecf04dad6bb1e96da971f80593aff1566cf411","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"（修訂版）32、：小心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老人：小明，你今天上班要小心！<br />\n<br />\n正在街上行走的小明，被不認識的老人家截停說，就感到十分不解，便問老人：「為什麼今天我要特別小心呢？」<br />\n<br />\n老人拉起自己的褲腳，露出義肢，說：「你知道嗎，我的腿變成這樣，就是因為你今天將會的意外。」"},{"pid":"7bdc3d8f0d9e09eca3032e77ef98455c9ce21434","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"33：好味<br />\n<br />\n小明：老闆，你這裏的牛腩麵特別好味。<br />\n<br />\n店主：當然，我們這裏的食材十分特別。<br />\n<br />\n一位廚師正在小明後面，正在一刀刀將他的皮肉割下來，拋進一大窩正在泡制的牛肉麵中。"},{"pid":"41ea6e7ee189e57fea519c5b9392f9b954cbdf06","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"34：情人<br />\n<br />\n小明：大衛，你就別傷心了，正所謂：「人死不能復生」。<br />\n<br />\n大衛：我不傷心就假了，我的太太今年才27歲，你看，她生前多美麗！<br />\n<br />\n大衛將手機遞給小明，螢光幕上顯示大衛太太的照片。<br />\n<br />\n小明馬上就嚇呆了，因為昨晚他才在夜店邂逅了這位女子，並享受了一晚魚水之歡。"},{"pid":"4943e715fcdacaa122d38e9cc7cd02ae1f20f073","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T23:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b326bd5fbf865458158a322f9e67cbaeeb0745f7","tid":36914,"uid":65425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0154e91e1241ecf1f990443f12f6d53aba030098","tid":36914,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"麻麻地"},{"pid":"4b139bb426d08e1afdb76a68b7107a71e36cfa3e","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麻麻地</blockquote><br />\n麻麻地，都要繼續睇"},{"pid":"8b47a31c72c1d744fc98cb670a238146e02dde53","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"25. 電話<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n小麗：小明，我好想念你！<br />\n<br />\n小麗說完，就上前擁著小麗。<br />\n<br />\n小明馬上嚇得把電話也跌在地上。<br />\n<br />\n小麗：小麗，你沒事嗎？<br />\n<br />\n跌在地上的電話，上面顯示著的正是小麗的電話號碼，聲筒依稀還能傳來小麗的聲音：「喂&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"fc7427d0b5892df7c369fab29a9729b061bb8743","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"小編越來越鐘意寫呢個post，因為好像是「正皮」和「負皮」的角力^^"},{"pid":"c7e7ffd4ad646961a85281521c651da8b434b257","tid":36914,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564dd8c62d9fd4f7bfc8ae26d21ff0b8d2b6e7f3","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n看來剛剛這個負皮是你俾的！"},{"pid":"a85592b05d99406cd90365946c6e12bed703edc2","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T00:06:25.000Z","msg":"26：葬禮<br />\n<br />\n今天去了一個葬禮，靈堂寫著我的名字。"},{"pid":"06441ab0909e26baa79791c6c3d0a774057683ab","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T00:07:27.000Z","msg":"27：醒來<br />\n<br />\n一早起來，發現自己活在六十年代。"},{"pid":"0116731d5f6bd90429b84f9b26374e3ae859d84b","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:32:51.000Z","msg":"28：今晚吃嘜餸<br />\n<br />\n老婆，今晚吃嘜餸？<br />\n<br />\n桌上還放著吃剩的晚餐。"},{"pid":"3b3c1210c8469bf88ccde663173d3b52d9c57fe4","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"29. 下一個到你<br />\n<br />\n小明今日參加一個葬禮，好不傷心。<br />\n<br />\n牧師卻跟他說：「別傷心，下一個便是你。」"},{"pid":"00680f591b5f2fbb78950e4be99c14162ff453c7","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>29. 下一個到你<br />\n<br />\n小明今日參加一個葬禮，好不傷心。<br />\n<br />\n牧師卻跟他說：「別傷心，下一個便是你。」</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"4ca1ef0c2c6b28e51d6f2145f00d89d408195a08","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:13:08.000Z","msg":"30：紅綠燈<br />\n<br />\n今天遇到一盞只有紅色和黃色的紅綠燈。"},{"pid":"0b0ad8aa1bc276e5a8a3475e628bdd4df67fda85","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"31 :回來吃飯<br />\n<br />\n媽：，今晚回來吃飯。<br />\n<br />\n兒：昨天已經回來吃了。"},{"pid":"20a11ae1893b6f58d3fb5eb1a0829da209e504e3","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:17:56.000Z","msg":"32：他她牠<br />\n<br />\n當他遇上她，多了一個牠。"},{"pid":"f7749b92de77da39f64745b1ab49f7a6e132f9e0","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:21:55.000Z","msg":"33：背影<br />\n<br />\n在倒後鏡中看見一個不認識的背影。"},{"pid":"9e0f8d398fea0690447af7c73088868d15ec0666","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"34：愛<br />\n<br />\n我愛你，你卻愛她"},{"pid":"e499559d654dcf077e1dfa19714417f0e2ed9c60","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"35:旅行<br />\n<br />\n兩個人去，三個人回。"},{"pid":"b653caf4404fd6c5be8d0b3c1ee4760edb22a720","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"35：左右手<br />\n<br />\n左手：右手，我愛你<br />\n<br />\n右手：我愛的是以前的左手"},{"pid":"b17d69d8009b815e0277233ad50b2c89ea59cc47","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"37：愛與恨<br />\n<br />\n我愛她，她恨我"},{"pid":"ad01efec6cb08b19bfb2195f640d263297c78fd9","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"38:戒指<br />\n<br />\n眾目之下，我送她戒指，她卻給我喜帖。"},{"pid":"708ba9511183a26828a49e0274fd8fed31a8e0c5","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:30:56.000Z","msg":"39：爸爸<br />\n<br />\n當差的爸爸約我晚上吃飯，但我們這頓飯永遠也無法吃完了。"},{"pid":"5f495c6808afc771fcfcd257c09975f9d7d846cb","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"40:  利是<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天老細派我一封利是，我卻給他一個大信封！"},{"pid":"ba9e2a5220c3ebbb8876111393b1d20e35a3165c","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"41：速度<br />\n<br />\n我如常開車由屯門出中環，下車時看手錶，發覺只用了五分鐘。"},{"pid":"aacb4e0fa81024b2d77f1f1c73ae35d629b40863","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"42: 魔術師<br />\n<br />\n魔術師邀請我太太上台表演後，她就再沒有回到我身邊。"},{"pid":"f202bfb71d5e02fd35fc9c301771c49424ecf9d7","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"43：老闆<br />\n<br />\n今日老闆叫我早點下班休息。我真的跟着辦,結果我明天再也不用上班了。"},{"pid":"a51777eab85fa62960ca4ff702570335c27bcc71","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"44：同義詞<br />\n<br />\n老闆、老婆丶老母 是同義詞"},{"pid":"9735b5f7dd5315cd9a88331633e85bf1772f8e97","tid":36914,"uid":63439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"45 :畫畫<br />\n<br />\n老師說我畫畫很靚，但其實我在寫字。"}]}